English:
@d0<color=#ff0000>Your orders are simple. Take over that communications station and change the market price data for {Eden_String}. Make it look like the price is skyrocketing. Then we can come in and sell our own {Eden_String} for a huge profit.</color>
@p9 @d0<color=#ff0000>Not to mention with everyone looking to buy them to get in on the market we'll make a killing raiding all those freighters!</color>
<color=#ff0000>Of course, spreading rumors about certain Traders Guild executives couldn't hurt either. Oh and do try not to kill anyone, you can use the hostages in case someone shows up to stop you.</color>
<color=#ff0000>- Korvax</color>

