English:
I was stationed on this freighter as a robotic medical assistant for the crew since the crew size did not require a full doctor.
While I am not privy to all the details, my understanding is that the ship was pulled out of warp into this dark matter nebula. The sudden collapse of the warp field drained the ship of all power and the crew were forced to evacuate to the life pods in a desperate attempt to survive.
@p9They left me behind since I do not require life support and have an independent power supply.
I can give you the frequencies for the life pod transponders, but you will need specialized scanning equipment to break through the interference of the dark matter nebula and get a fix on their positions.
@p9I estimate their oxygen will run out soon so it will be a race against the clock for you to find them in time.
Before they left, the captain authorized me to provide payment to any who are able to mount a rescue, with payment based on how many of the surviving crew you can rescue.

Chinese (simplified):
我被派驻在这艘货轮上担任船员的机器人医疗助理,因为船员的规模不需要全职医生.
虽然我并不清楚所有细节,但按照我的理解,这艘船被拉出了翘曲空间,进入了这个暗物质星云。翘曲场的突然崩溃耗尽了飞船的所有动力,船员们被迫撤离到救生舱拼死求生。.
@p9 由于我不需要生命支持并且拥有独立的电源,他们便抛下了我.
我可以把你生命舱转发器的频率发给你,但是你需要专门的扫描设备来突破暗物质星云的干扰并确定它们的位置.
@p9 我估计他们的氧气很快就会耗尽,所以你动作必须得足够快才能及时找到他们.
B在他们离开之前,舰长授权我向任何能够进行救援的人提供酬劳,金额取决于您可以救援多少幸存船员.

