English:
@d0<color=#ffff00>Log 147-2:</color>
<color=#ff8000>We took on a Doctor Weston from the colony who had fallen ill under mysterious circumstances. We had been cannibalizing the ship for spare parts to continue building the colony, but had not yet removed the medical bay so they sent him up to us to treat.</color>
@p9 @d0<color=#ff8000>All I know is red alert was issued and the captain sealed off the bridge with his personal command code and initiated the self destruct sequence.</color>
<color=#ff8000>Something went wrong and only 2 of the secondary generators blew. There were power surges but most of the ship is intact. If any U.C.H officers are reading this, you might be able to get some systems operational.</color>
@p9 @d0<color=#ff8000>You've no doubt already turned on the auxiliary generators. The gravity controls are on the other side of this room. Turn both switches to the on position, but to fully enable gravity you'll need to find the conduit bypass deeper in the ship. </color>
<color=#ff8000>You might be able to access the bridge if you search the captain's quarters for his personal over-ride.</color>
<color=#ff8000>I hear screams now. Nightmarish screams. I don't even blame the captain for wanting to destroy the ship. May the other ships of Project Eden find greener pastures...</color>

