@d3 <color=#00fbff>当然,指挥官。@w2 这似乎是一个基础锁。民用运输工具的标准配置。应该很容易绕过。@w2 并且...@w2 完成了。@w2 你现在可以访问你的装备了。只有一个小问题...</color>
@p9 <color=#00fbff>军械库中没有盔甲箱来帮助你穿上标准发行的中型盔甲。你接下来真的需要那件盔甲。</color>
@w2 <color=#00fbff>好消息是走廊对面有一个医疗舱,那里很可能有一个盔甲箱。@w3 坏消息是走廊现在已经减压,你将不得不跑到医疗舱并穿上你的盔甲,以免窒息。</color>
@w3 <color=#00fbff>你屏住呼吸的能力有多强?</color>

English:
@q0 @d0<b><color=#fafe10>[ IDA ]</color></b>
@d3<color=#00fbff>Sarcasm aside, the last thing stored in my memory banks is that you were captured by the Zirax empire.</color>@w2<color=#00fbff>At that time I shut down completely in order to avoid detection. It seems the empire did a sloppy job and didn't detect my hardware.</color>
@w3<color=#00fbff>I have no knowledge of any events after that. I assume you had a trial and were found guilty?</color>
@p9 @d0<color=#1083fe><b>[ {PlayerName} ]</b></color>
@d3If you could call it a trial. @w2My defense attorney was an alien who I couldn't understand and the judge announced that I was guilty 20 minutes into the trial.
@w2I was sentenced to life without parole on a penal colony near the edge of Zirax territory. I was put onto a transport.
@p9 @d0<color=#1083fe><b>[ {PlayerName} ]</b></color>
@d3Shortly after, all of this happened. @w2All I remember was a sudden jolt then everything went black. It felt like a rapid deceleration.
@w2Wait, @w1if you shut yourself down, @w1then how are you online now?

Chinese (simplified):
@q0 @d0 <b><color=#fafe10>[ IDA ]</color></b>
@d3 <color=#00fbff>讽刺的话先放一边,我记忆中最后一件事是你被兹瑞克斯帝国俘虏了。</color>@w2 <color=#00fbff>那时我完全关闭了,以避免被发现。看来帝国工作不够细致,没有检测到我的硬件。</color>
@w3 <color=#00fbff>我没有任何那之后事件的知识。我猜你经过了审判并被判有罪?</color>
@p9 @d0 <color=#1083fe><b>[ {PlayerName} ]</b></color>
@d3 如果你能称之为审判的话。@w2 我的辩护律师是一个我听不懂的外星人,法官在审判开始20分钟后宣布我有罪。
@w2 我被判处在兹瑞克斯领土边缘的监狱殖民地终身监禁,不得假释。我被放到了一艘运输船上。
@p9 @d0 <color=#1083fe><b>[ {PlayerName} ]</b></color>
@d3 不久之后,这一切就发生了。@w2 我所记得的就是突然的震动,然后一切都变黑了。感觉像是快速减速。
@w2 等等,@w1 如果你关闭了自己,@w1 那你现在怎么在线?

