@q0 @d0<b><color=#fafe10>[ IDA ]</color></b>
@d3<color=#00fbff>A good question. @w2The crash must have damaged your suit, activating a failsafe that brought me back online for emergency situations.</color>
@w2<color=#00fbff>My assessment has determined that this may be one of those situations.</color>
@p9<color=#00fbff>As for why we have crashed, @w1based on your recollection of events, @w1the most likely scenario is that the ship encountered an unexpected gravitational anomaly, @w2such as a black hole or rogue planet, @w1that pulled the ship out of warp and caused massive damage in the process.</color>
@w2<color=#00fbff>This could be good news for you.</color>

