If you are able to hack into the system you may be able to extract valuable data from it.</color>
@p9 @d3<color=#00fbff>Many factions or organizations would set up satellites like these throughout the galaxy for science, communications, and even military operations.</color> @w2<color=#00fbff>They are unlikely to be guarded, @w2no one will know if you attempt to hack them.</color>
@w2<color=#00fbff>You will likely find these satellites in a central position within a star system, @w1such as in the sun warp sectors you arrive in when you first warp to a star system, @w1or placed near anomalies to study them such as this satellite is.</color>
@p9 @d3<color=#00fbff>I can interface with the satellite's computer for you now if you'd like. @w1Once you have completed or failed the hack, @w1the system will go into lockdown and you will be unable to access it again.</color>
