English:
@d0Directions for safe use of the Prototype Micro Jump Drive:
1: Place a Prototype Micro Jump Drive on your Small Vessel or Capital Vessel. The drive should be kept OFF at all times as it will be automatically turned ON and OFF by the computer. Do not rename the Prototype Micro Jump Drive in the control panel.
2: Place Refined Pentaxid in your personal inventory. The Prototype Micro Jump Drive cannot use pentaxid from a Pentaxid Tank.
@p9 @d03: Pilot a Small Vessel or Capital Vessel while in space. You cannot make micro jumps while on a planet or moon or as a passenger.
4: Aim where you want to jump. The micro jump drive attempts to jump forward. You can jump into or through planets or other obstacles, but if your jump would land you too close to another object the jump will fail.
@p9 @d05: There are two ways to initiate the micro jump:
- From the control panel, select the Prototype Micro Jump Drive and click the ACCESS button. After a moment the jump drive interface will open. Do NOT turn it on in the control panel, the drive's power state will be controlled by the computer automatically. Once you initiate the jump sequence sit back and enjoy the ride!
- From the tutorial tab of the PDA, activate the Micro Jump Drive Activation mission to open the jump drive interface and follow the instructions once you have initiated the jump sequence.
@p9 @d0<color=#ff0000>Note that due to a game bug you will need to restart your game before you can use the micro jump drive with any ship that has changed playfields during this play session. For example if you take your ship from planet to orbit, or warp your ship from one sector to another, you will need to restart your game before the micro jump drive will work on that ship.</color>

Chinese (simplified):
@d0 原型微型跳跃驱动器的安全使用指南:
1: 将一个原型微型跳跃驱动器放置在您的小型飞船或主力舰上。驱动器应始终保持关闭状态,因为它将由计算机自动开启和关闭。不要在控制面板中重命名原型微型跳跃驱动器。
2: 将精炼翘曲水晶放入您的个人库存中。原型微型跳跃驱动器不能使用翘曲水晶罐中的翘曲水晶。
@p9 @d0 3: 在太空中驾驶小型飞船或主力舰。您不能在行星或月球上或作为乘客时进行微型跳跃。
4: 瞄准您想要跳跃的位置。微型跳跃驱动器尝试向前跳跃。您可以跳入或穿过行星或其他障碍物,但如果您的跳跃会使您太靠近另一个物体,跳跃将失败。
@p9 @d0 5: 有三种方式启动微型跳跃:
- 从控制面板中,选择原型微型跳跃驱动器并点击ACCESS按钮。稍后,跳跃驱动器界面将打开。不要在控制面板中打开它,驱动器的电源状态将由计算机自动控制。一旦您启动了跳跃序列,就坐下来享受旅程吧!
- 从PDA的教程标签中,激活微型跳跃驱动器激活任务以打开跳跃驱动器界面,并在启动跳跃序列后按照指示操作。
@p9 @d0 <color=#ff0000>请注意,由于游戏漏洞,您需要在当前游戏会话中更改过场地的任何飞船使用微型跳跃驱动器之前重新启动游戏。例如,如果您将飞船从行星带到轨道,或者将飞船从一个星区翘曲到另一个星区,您需要在该飞船上的微型跳跃驱动器工作之前重新启动游戏。</color>

