English:
@q0<color=#ff0000>The core of a main story mission POI has been destroyed.
Within Reforged Eden 2, the cores of main story mission POIs cannot normally be destroyed.</color>
<color=#ffff00></color>
<color=#ffff00>This means either an admin used console commands to destroy the admin core, or the scenario's configuration files have been modified away from the Reforged Eden 2 defaults to allow admin cores to be destroyed.</color>
@p9<color=#ff0000>Playing with modified configuration files is NOT supported by the Reforged Eden 2 developers.</color>
<color=#ff0000>Do not seek assistance with any issues you encounter while playing with modified configuration files as they will not be able to assist you.</color>
<color=#ff0000>You risk breaking missions, progression, and other problems with the removal of admin core protection.</color>
@p9<color=#ff0000>If you continue to play using this save game AND OR continue to play using any modified configuration files, you do so AT YOUR OWN RISK.</color>
<color=#ff0000>The Reforged Eden 2 developers will not be able to offer you any assistance for any broken missions or progression as a result of using modified configuration files.</color>

<color=#ffff00>DO YOU UNDERSTAND?</color>

