<color=#ff0000>Reforged Eden 2的开发者将无法为您提供因使用修改后的配置文件而导致的任何破坏的任务或进展的任何帮助。</color>

<color=#ffff00>您理解了吗?</color>

English:
@q0Removing admin core protection means that main story mission POIs will no longer be protected, allowing you to destroy important mission-related consoles or devices or remove the core or damage the structure.
This may break missions and prevent you from completing them.
It may also lock you out of certain progression within the scenario or cause other issues.
@p9The Reforged Eden 2 developers cannot assist with any issues that arise as normally you cannot destroy the core of these story mission POIs.
If you are playing on a server or using a scenario that wasn't created by the Reforged Eden 2 developers, please seek assistance from your server admin or the author of the scenario you are currently playing.

Chinese (simplified):
@q0移除管理员核心保护意味着主线任务POI将不再受到保护,允许您破坏与任务相关的重要控制台或设备,或者移除核心或损坏结构。
这可能会破坏任务并阻止您完成任务。
它还可能锁定您在场景中的某些进展或导致其他问题。
@p9Reforged Eden 2的开发者无法协助解决因通常不允许破坏这些主线任务POI的核心而出现的问题。
如果您在服务器上玩或使用不是由Reforged Eden 2开发者创建的场景,请向您的服务器管理员或您当前正在玩的场景的作者寻求帮助。

English:
@q0Commander {Player.Name}, @w1we received a troubling message from a representative of the Trade Federation.
@w2This individual is asking for our help to investigate something that happened near the Sea of Silence.
@w2In case you are not aware, that region of space has been blockaded by the Zirax Empire in an effort to contain the Legacy from spreading out into the galaxy. @w2 While this mission will be exploratory in nature, @w1 you may encounter dangerous situations that put your ship at risk.
@w2To put it bluntly, @w1 don't fly what you can't afford to lose.

Chinese (simplified):
@q0指挥官 {Player.Name},@w1我们从贸易联合会的代表那里收到了一条令人不安的消息。
@w2这个人请求我们帮助调查在沉默之海附近发生的一些事情。
@w2如果你不知道,那个太空区域已经被兹瑞克斯帝国封锁,以阻止遗留者扩散到银河系中。@w2虽然这个任务将是探索性的,@w1你可能会遭遇危险的情况,使你的飞船处于风险之中。
@w2坦白说,@w1不要飞你输不起的东西。

English:
@q0There have been questions raised regarding the resources being sent to the Zirax blockade at The Bulwark.
@w2Every year there has been an increase in funding allocated to the Andromeda Defense at The Bulwark that watches over the Sea of Silence. @w1Certain members of the Trade Federation's Board of Executives feel this funding would be put to better use elsewhere given the complete lack of activity observed in the Sea of Silence.
@p9 @d3My brother was sent to perform an audit of the activities at The Bulwark to find out if the increased funding was necessary.
@w2Unfortunately, @w1no one has heard from him for weeks. @w1I have exhausted nearly all my contacts within the Trade Federation and Zirax Empire and thus far none have been able to give me much to go on.

Chinese (simplified):
@q0有关送往The Bulwark的Zirax封锁线的资源问题已经引起了质疑。
@w2每年分配给监视沉默之海的仙女座防御The Bulwark的资金都在增加。@w1贸易联合会执行委员会的某些成员认为,鉴于在沉默之海观察到的完全缺乏活动,这些资金可以更好地用在其他地方。
@p9 @d3我的兄弟被派去审计The Bulwark的活动,以找出增加的资金是否必要。
@w2不幸的是,@w1几周来没有人听到过他的消息。@w1我已经用尽了我在贸易联合会和Zirax帝国的几乎所有联系人,到目前为止还没有人能给我提供太多线索。

English:
@q0Oh, @w1but I am on a proper escort ship! @w2At least as far as the rest of the board knows.
@w2My ship should be halfway to Kelsar Prime by now to visit my sick cousin, Xor'Ataltha.
@w2I don't have a cousin named Xor'Ataltha. @w1By the time anyone notices the discrepancy in my family tree you and I will have found my brother and we'll both be back aboard my luxury space yacht The Promised Path.
@p9 @d3As for why I am flying this hunk of junk? @w2I had to improvise. @w1What one does when they are desperate.
@w2I needed a ship that wouldn't raise eyebrows or show up on any ship registries so I bought one at a scrapyard.

Chinese (simplified):
@q0哦,@w1但我确实在一艘正规的护卫舰上!@w2至少就董事会其他人所知。
@w2我的飞船现在应该已经飞到Kelsar Prime的一半路程,去看望我生病的堂兄Xor'Ataltha。
